      <p class="paragraph">
        A roguelike adventure game that runs entirely in the terminal. Navigate procedurally generated dungeons, manage resources, and search for the legendary Ever-Burning Lamp. Built with TypeScript and Bun, featuring A* pathfinding, field-of-view shadowcasting, and local database persistence for game state.
      </p>

      <p class="paragraph">
        The game requires Truecolor terminal support and runs on macOS.
      </p>

